<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Test Email</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; background-color:
      #f4f4f4; } .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto;
      background-color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0
      4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); } h2 { color: #333; } p { color: #666;
      line-height: 1.5; } li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>Greetings from Our Test Email!</h2>
      <p>Hello {{name}}!</p>
      <p>We're thrilled to have you as part of our community. This is a test
        email crafted to check the efficiency of our mailing system. Our aim is
        to continuously improve our service and provide you with the best
        communication experience.</p>
      <p>Key points of this email:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Delivery check.</li>
        <li>Text and image formatting.</li>
        <li>Feedback from recipients.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>If you have any suggestions or comments regarding this message, please
        let us know. Your feedback is highly valuable to us!</p>
      <p>Warm regards,<br />
        {{senderName}}</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>